  <section class="hero"><div class="wrap">
          <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/brands/">Brands</a> › Follett Ice Machine Repair</div>
          <h1>Follett Ice Machine Repair</h1>
          <p class="lede">
            Horizon Elite countertop nugget ice, Maestro Plus modular, Symphony Plus dispensers, REF and ITS
