  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>Where our Follett ice machine repair calls come from across Los Angeles</h2>
      <p class="intro">Same-day Follett service across LA hospital systems, fast-casual chains, and the surrounding regions:</p>
      <div class="area-grid">
        <div>
          <h4>Westwood / UCLA corridor</h4>
          <p>UCLA Ronald Reagan · Mattel Children's · UCLA medical offices · private surgical centers</p>
        </div>
        <div>
